Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.89,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对圣母玛利亚 保·密·哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.56,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.13,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.41,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了呢  佑巳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.17,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:26.38,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想给姐姐打个电话为今天的事致谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.90,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却不知道会是哪一位来接听
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:31.20,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不是那么轻易就能打出去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.80,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是福泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.09,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错而给挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:43.27,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉着一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.45,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.90,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天就能再与最喜欢的姐姐相见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.20,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然今天是如此愉快的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.85,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天也一定会是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.47,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是我与姐姐的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:12.47,zhengwenscn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  姐姐
